}

### Complete Habit
PATCH http://localhost:8080/daily-tasks/1/complete
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/daily-tasks
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE